data.name: TextBox2.Text
data.value: Primary focuser settings are available at the next tab. More astrohub settings are available in popup window when connected to ASCOM driver with any 3rd party focusing software (MaxIm, APT, FocusMax). Please enable popup window above to access these settings.

data.name: TextBox1.Text
data.value: Use it if you want to set current focser position, when you loose synchronization between focuser and driver. For example move focuser to its most inward position and then set position to 0.
